oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Aubrey Moncrief Interview
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Moncrief, Aubrey; Caudill, Ed
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Moncrief, Aubrey; Vietnam War, 1961-1975
